comments: Finney-Smith (BKN) jumps alongside of Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) brings his off-arm toward Finney-Smith's (BKN) side and marginal contact occurs as Jokic (DEN) attempts to dribble around Finney-Smith (BKN) during the drive.
Jokic (DEN) places his collapsing forearm to Finney-Smith's (BKN) backside and marginal body contact occurs underneath the basket.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) brings his arm toward Dinwiddie's (BKN) path and marginal contact occurs during Dinwiddie's (BKN) drive.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) establishes himself in Finney-Smith's (BKN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Finney-Smith (BKN) briefly places his hand to Jokic's (DEN) side as Finney-Smith brushes Jokic's wrist and Jokic is able to move through the marginal contact to gather the pass.
Dinwiddie (BKN) initiates contact with Jokic's (DEN) body, and applies force that affects his driving shot attempt.
Finney-Smith (BKN) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and does not deliver contact.
Jokic (DEN) legally contests Dinwiddie's (BKN) jump shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs after his release.
Finney-Smith (BKN) is moving alongside Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs during Jokic's drive.
Finney-Smith (BKN) and Jokic (DEN) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) elbow makes contact with the ball after Dinwiddie's (BKN) gather and dislodges the ball away before incidental arm contact occurs.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly given to BKN.
Finney-Smith (BKN) establishes himself in Brown's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as Brown defends under the pick.
Braun (DEN) places his forearm to Dinwiddie's (BKN) front after his gather and cleanly dislodges Dinwiddie's (BKN) driving shot attempt before incidental arm contact occurs.
Dinwiddie (BKN) brings his off-arm outward and marginal contact occurs with Braun (DEN) during the driving shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (BKN) moves laterally into Jokic's (DEN) path and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Braun (DEN) brings his arm toward Dinwiddie's (BKN) side and marginal contact occurs during Dinwiddie's drive.

Replay review of the foul called on Jokic (DEN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Dinwiddie (BKN) flails his off-arm outward and delivers contact to Jokic's (DEN) face that affects Jokic's ability to defend.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) establishes himself in O'Neale's (BKN) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Dinwiddie (BKN) jumps along Brown's (DEN) path and dislodges Brown's driving shot attempt before incidental contact occurs.
Brown (DEN) brings his off-arm outward and marginal contact occurs with Dinwiddie (BKN) during the driving shot attempt.
O'Neale (BKN) moves along Jokic's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together at the start of Jokic's drive.
O'Neale (BKN) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball as Jokic gathers the entry pass.
O'Neale (BKN) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly given to DEN.
Dinwiddie (BKN) places his forearm to Jokic's (DEN) front and slides his arm off without applying force during Jokic's shot attempt.
Finney-Smith (BKN) and Gordon (DEN) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Following the loose ball, Brown (DEN) reaches around Johnson's (BKN) body and affects his SQBR.
Dinwiddie (BKN) and Dinwiddie (BKN) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Brown (DEN) briefly grasps Bridges' (BKN) arm and immediately slides his hand off as Bridges' gathers the entry pass.
Dinwiddie (BKN) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Brown (DEN) commits a take foul on Bridges' (BKN).
O'Neale (BKN) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
